            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特斯拉巨鯨廖凱原買入100萬股輝達 將再買100萬股以支持緊張的市場\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1364\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6Zh1XpAjfq2Reio2tFX_GQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzNjQ-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/1fb3ae00-17d8-11f1-affe-340afb7e2b65\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特斯拉巨鯨廖凱原買入100萬股輝達 將再買100萬股以支持緊張的市場</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
